lyrics:
[Verse]
Darkness descends upon the Belgian shore
Where the seagulls gather, their screams galore
A contest of madness, with feathers as the crown
To be the champion, their screeches resound

[Chorus]
Unholy echoes pierce the night, chaos embraced
As the seagulls rise, the seagulls take their place
In the blackened skies, their reign forever claimed
Belgium's new seagull screeching champion is proclaimed
